    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Discretization error GCI < 5%, output comparison error < 15%, and RH < 1 acceptance criterion satisfied across all 5 operating points. The computational model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions for the Class II CPB device within the defined COU.",
